thread.title: Karen

author: Karen
title: Karen
text: I started with City Finance Townsville, however, due to unforseen circumstances, the Townsville office closed down. I always received excellent service with the Townsville office and when i needed assistance again, i went online. The Mackay City Finance office were as quick, easy and friendly as the Townsville branch. They have been an excellent service and one i will continue to use as the need arises.
